Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.89,0:02:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们曾是我的憧憬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.56,0:02:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们看起来其乐融融
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.82,0:02:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散发着一股自豪感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.16,0:02:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去炫彩夺目…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.75,0:02:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.59,0:02:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要像这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.92,0:03:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经脱胎换骨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.26,0:03:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.46,0:04:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁是矢俣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.13,0:04:19.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问谁是矢俣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.38,0:04:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八咫鸦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.38,0:04:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.14,0:04:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打着吠舞罗…  打着尊哥的旗号做了不少好事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.60,0:04:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思  我也是吠舞罗的一员啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.15,0:04:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也…  我也是赤之氏族啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.91,0:04:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲  来客人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.62,0:04:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.49,0:04:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许动  我们是Scepter4
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.71,0:04:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.21,0:05:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要这样对我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.85,0:05:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我使用了这份得到手的“力量”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.02,0:05:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用了现在的身份立场  只为往上爬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.07,0:05:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了获胜  为了出人头地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.79,0:05:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.30,0:05:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,矢俣大智
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.97,0:05:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找了你很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.47,0:05:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.69,0:05:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想听听你的解释
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.02,0:06:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我想和你谈谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.07,0:06:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能跟我走一趟吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.58,0:06:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王？你怎么会在这
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是矢俣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.42,0:06:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下王  首先要和他谈一谈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.42,0:06:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.63,0:06:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被街上的小混混狠狠揍了一顿后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.47,0:06:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说“想要变强”“不想再被欺负了”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.43,0:06:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就跑来加入我们了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.52,0:06:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您还记得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.98,0:06:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你就从“被欺负”转变成“欺负人”了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.53,0:06:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.16,0:06:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没打算责备他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.75,0:06:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想挨打  就要先下手为强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想被他人掠夺就先抢夺他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.63,0:07:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.09,0:07:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.88,0:07:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.89,0:07:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从别人手上抢来的东西  总有一天会被他人夺走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.68,0:07:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.65,0:07:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我顺便告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.11,0:07:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真正想要的不是这份能操纵火焰的“力量”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.78,0:07:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是要成为吠舞罗的成员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.79,0:07:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是从别人那里抢来的利益
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.29,0:07:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真正想要的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.05,0:07:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是自尊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.10,0:08:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.56,0:08:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也是我这份“力量”的牺牲者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.44,0:08:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.32,0:08:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆就让吠舞罗散伙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.62,0:08:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思是解散吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.34,0:08:29.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.59,0:08:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这样危险的王是需要一个容身之地的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.18,0:08:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个让你睡睡午觉  吃个饭  有时还能找个乐子的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.27,0:08:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是为了你  而是为了世人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.15,0:08:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关世人什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.36,0:08:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就当是为了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.00,0:09:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先和大家谈一谈吧  然后再…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.21,0:09:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了  在这
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.55,0:09:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Scepter4？他们怎么会来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.34,0:09:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.81,0:09:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才失礼了  赤王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.98,0:09:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据Scepter4的业务  有必要找你们的矢俣了解情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.82,0:09:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能把他交给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.53,0:09:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我滚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.62,0:09:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  你不爱下命令的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.99,0:09:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.66,0:09:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.09,0:09:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好  全员…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.93,0:10:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说中力量强大的赤王居然会先攻击我的氏族成员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.44,0:10:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上你的兴趣是欺凌弱者吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.86,0:10:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着一群手下跑来闹事  你还有脸说这话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.87,0:10:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.25,0:10:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在为朋友争取逃跑时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.71,0:10:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是感人肺腑的友情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.13,0:10:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淡岛  不好意思  劳烦你去抓回那两个逃跑的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.42,0:10:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但室长您…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.22,0:10:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有我一个就足够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.14,0:10:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.60,0:10:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.68,0:10:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.37,0:11:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔刀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.17,0:11:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  你不会用刀啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.13,0:11:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对付一个无法无天的流氓  拔刀就有点小题大做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.47,0:11:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一让你受了重伤  我可是会于心不忍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.72,0:11:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吊我胃口也是一件好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.02,0:11:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果你只是耍耍嘴皮子  那我可不会轻易放过你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.73,0:11:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就用不着你来操心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.84,0:12:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.60,0:12:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鉴于之前的“迦具都事件”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.14,0:12:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王与王之间正面交锋并不是上策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.19,0:12:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优先确保抓住矢俣大智
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.56,0:12:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此之前随便应付一下这个男人  拖住他就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.92,0:12:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.63,0:12:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  你真是出乎我的期待啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.01,0:12:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有两下子啊  宗像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.68,0:12:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.10,0:12:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从正面冲上来？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.56,0:12:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是愚蠢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.26,0:13:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  新人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.14,0:13:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没玩够呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.39,0:13:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.35,0:13:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他这个王权者并不只是摆着好看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.33,0:13:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是脑补了我满身泥土匍匐在地的样子啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.18,0:14:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你个死脑筋的书呆子还挺灵活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.97,0:14:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那一下流氓飞踢也粗野
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.74,0:14:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.84,0:14:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.85,0:14:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去没完没了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.81,0:14:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行吧  算我输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.98,0:15:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,矢俣大智先交给你们吠舞罗处理吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.94,0:15:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就到此为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.92,0:15:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都认输了你还想怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.13,0:15:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是  从来没有人会让我如此不爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.26,0:15:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.51,0:15:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想干什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.93,0:15:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想干什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.60,0:15:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是把看不顺眼的家伙痛扁一顿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.77,0:15:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你疯了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.11,0:15:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.63,0:16:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们去那边搜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.96,0:16:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.44,0:16:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.92,0:16:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男人到底有什么问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.42,0:16:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,室长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.97,0:16:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我失态了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.89,0:16:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淡岛  矢俣大智抓到了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.18,0:17:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  非常抱歉 还没有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.10,0:17:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.06,0:17:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拜托各位继续搜查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.36,0:17:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请…请问赤…周防尊呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.95,0:17:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.16,0:17:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男人由我负责压制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.12,0:17:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要心急  保持一定距离围住他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.50,0:17:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  这群家伙真会躲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.76,0:17:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲  别太拼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.38,0:17:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.39,0:17:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草薙哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.98,0:17:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  长时间没收到十束的联络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.94,0:17:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点担心就过来看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.69,0:17:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退  重整队列
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.99,0:17:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草薙哥  真是帮大忙啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.95,0:17:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是来帮你们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.70,0:18:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是叫你们老实点吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.37,0:18:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是对方先动手的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.21,0:18:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关键的矢悟呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.21,0:18:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.96,0:18:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么十束呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.92,0:18:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没看见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.88,0:18:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你们两位就和蓝衣服的打架啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.97,0:18:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的让我省点心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.26,0:18:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.64,0:18:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草薙哥  那个难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.11,0:18:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是尊吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.25,0:18:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你  王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.51,0:19:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最后的警告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.76,0:19:45.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周防尊  收起你的剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.18,0:19:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这表情真不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.48,0:19:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔刀吧  宗像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.90,0:20:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾等Scepter4  将执行佩剑者职务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.04,0:20:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣域不容纷扰  现世不容暴力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.71,0:20:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以剑制剑  吾等大义毫无阴霾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.22,0:20:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗像  拔刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.52,0:20:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鉴于前任的恩怨  剑下坠了怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.95,0:20:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管谁的剑  我都不会让它下坠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.45,0:20:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还打算连我的剑一起管吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.70,0:20:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你的手脚砍飞三四条就能就解决的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.75,0:20:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真豪迈啊  听着还挺痛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.88,0:21:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可真是个无可救药的疯子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.64,0:21:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.76,0:21:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然被选为王  为什么不尽你的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.56,0:21:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关我什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.97,0:21:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要被什么破烂使命束缚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.32,0:21:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到力量的人应该正确行使自身的责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.49,0:21:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份责任是为了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.79,0:21:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有谁在期望我负担责任？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.10,0:21:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周防  你的这份傲慢就是强者的骄傲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.90,0:22:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否强大是由自身决定的  岂能被他人左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.61,0:22:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然是在对牛弹琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.41,0:22:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过  只会考虑自己标准的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.66,0:22:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算脑子转得再快  也只是个笨蛋啊  宗像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.27,0:22:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗像  我看你很不顺眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.65,0:22:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真巧啊  周防
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.53,0:22:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是这么想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.49,0:22:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要拧断你的脖子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.04,0:22:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把你大卸八块
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.12,0:22:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待看你哭丧著脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.04,0:23:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待看你对我跪地求饶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.72,0:23:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.55,0:23:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来就来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.49,0:23:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水火相争  阴阳之巅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.46,0:23:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.04,0:23:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤王周防尊  青王宗像礼司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.75,0:23:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是无色之王  三轮一言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.38,0:23:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是七王之间的调停人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.93,0:23:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接受黄金之王  国常路大觉的委托  迟来拜访了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.77,0:24:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你无关  快滚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.24,0:24:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们现在不能在这里“解决”恩怨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.43,0:24:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非时院负责善后的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.44,0:24:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,矢俣大智归赤之氏族管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.57,0:24:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但今后若吠舞罗的下级成员还有出格的行为  Scepter4将予以管理…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.66,0:24:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对御前的裁决无任何异议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.41,0:25:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:02.08,0:25:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么好谈的了  我回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.88,0:25:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  赤王看上去很疲惫啊  之前果然是太拼了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.80,0:25:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为遇到了一件很恶心的事 昨天喝了一晚上的酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:19.43,0:25:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这样真的好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:22.85,0:25:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不需要惩罚我们吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:25.73,0:25:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惩罚什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:29.03,0:25:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王权者之间的战斗行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:32.03,0:25:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能会招致王权爆发的危险行为的相应惩罚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:38.87,0:25:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于被石板所选中的王权者的行为  事后追责也毫无意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:46.17,0:25:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  一二零协定是禁止王之间无意义的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:52.97,0:25:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且协定的盟主就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:56.59,0:25:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请各位别忘记这项事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:05.44,0:26:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  我一旦遇到令人不爽的事就容易健忘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:11.11,0:26:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在能理解的范围内  还是能遵守的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:14.03,0:26:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  天也有不测风云嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:19.28,0:26:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:19.95,0:26:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,室长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:29.88,0:26:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们果然都是王啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:45.69,0:26:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就是新任的赤王和青王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:53.86,0:26:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟会…